kingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182780509/image_182780509.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182780509/image_182780509.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182780509/image_182780509.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182780509/image_182780509.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182780509/image_182780509.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">visual7</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Although US equities are mostly flat today, South Korean equities have been much more eventful. News broke today that the country's President Yoon Suk Yeol declared martial law, which was then contested by the National Assembly shortly thereafter. The catalyst for the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182780509/image_182780509.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741951-south-korea-etf-reaching-new-lows", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 08:30:00"}, {"id": "4741943", "title": "The U.S. Is A Booming Economy", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455167761/image_1455167761.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Growing the business together\" data-id=\"1455167761\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455167761/image_1455167761.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455167761/image_1455167761.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455167761/image_1455167761.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455167761/image_1455167761.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455167761/image_1455167761.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455167761/image_1455167761.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455167761/image_1455167761.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455167761/image_1455167761.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">pixelfit</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>\"Donald Trump will inherit a booming U.S. economy.\"</p> <p>So writes Valentina Romei, William Crofton, and Colby Smith in the <a href=\"https://www.ft.com/content/1201f834-6407-4bb5-ac9d-18496ec2948b\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.ft.com/content/1201f834-6407-4bb5-ac9d-18496ec2948b\" target=\"_blank\">Financial Times.</a></p> <p>The U.S. GDP \"has expanded by 11.4 percent since the end of 2019 and in its latest forecast, the IMF predicted U.S. growth</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455167761/image_1455167761.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741943-the-us-is-a-booming-economy", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 08:26:39"}, {"id": "4741949", "title": "Columbia Capital Allocation Portfolios Q3 2024 Commentary", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1389343192/image_1389343192.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Asse